---
/**
 * CostFactors.astro
 * Component explaining the various factors that affect furnace repair pricing
 */
---

<div class="space-y-8">
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">
    What Affects Your Final Cost?
  </h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path d="M7 3a1 1 0 000 2h6a1 1 0 100-2H7zM4 7a1 1 0 011-1h10a1 1 0 110 2H5a1 1 0 01-1-1zM2 11a2 2 0 012-2h12a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H4a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4z"/>
        </svg>
        Parts & Labor Required
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Some issues need simple fixes, others require expensive components
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
        Urgency Level
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Emergency after-hours service costs more than scheduled appointments
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.49 3.17c-.38-1.56-2.6-1.56-2.98 0a1.532 1.532 0 01-2.286.948c-1.372-.836-2.942.734-2.106 2.106.54.886.061 2.042-.947 2.287-1.561.379-1.561 2.6 0 2.978a1.532 1.532 0 01.947 2.287c-.836 1.372.734 2.942 2.106 2.106a1.532 1.532 0 012.287.947c.379 1.561 2.6 1.561 2.978 0a1.533 1.533 0 012.287-.947c1.372.836 2.942-.734 2.106-2.106a1.533 1.533 0 01.947-2.287c1.561-.379 1.561-2.6 0-2.978a1.532 1.532 0 01-.947-2.287c.836-1.372-.734-2.942-2.106-2.106a1.532 1.532 0 01-2.287-.947zM10 13a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
        System Age & Complexity
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Older systems or multi-zone setups may take longer to diagnose and repair
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"/>
        </svg>
        Provider Type
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Full-service companies and independent techs have different overhead structures
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
        Warranty Coverage
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Extended warranties and premium service plans affect overall pricing
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
        Local Market Conditions
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Detroit metro vs. rural areas may have slight price variations
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      That's why we start with a $125 diagnosis. Our licensed tech examines your system, identifies the exact issue, and presents you with transparent pricing from qualified providers that match your needs and budget.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>